      <th style="text-align: left">Hit Points</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: center">1st</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">1d10 + cavalier level</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">10th</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">4d10 + cavalier level</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: center">3rd</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">2d10 + cavalier level</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">15th</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">5d10 + cavalier level</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: center">7th</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">3d10 + cavalier level</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">18th</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">6d10 + cavalier level</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p>Once you use this feature, you must finish a short or long rest before you can use it again.</p>
